task.summary:
Client -Game is started by a driver, driver is brought to driver view, then an associated gunner is automatically brought to the gunner view -Gunner view controls the angle of the gun on the server and can press a button to fire the gun. TODO multi-touch currently broken
Server -Refactored socket management system, now uses select.select -Refactored Blob, now uses QGraphicsPixmapItems instead of QLabels -Refactored Board, now uses a QGraphicsView and a scene -Allows 2 clients to connect and play the game, order of connection is irrelevant. -Gunner client can control the angle of the gun attachted to a blob -Gunner client can control the firing of a projectile, said projectile appears at the correct point and has the correct direction of motion. TODO Speed of projectile will probably need updated.
